Memeburn.com &#x201c;It&#x2019;s live TV designed for the YouTube generation &#x2014; those who want to watch what they want, when they want, how they want, without commitments,&#x201d; reads the blog post. Working with networks and affiliate partners, YouTube has found a way to live stream from channels like ABC, CBS, FOX, NBC and ESPN &#x2014; meaning that viewers will be able to watch live as soon as a new episode of shows like Empire, Scandal and The Big Bang Theory airs. Read more on Memeburn.com.